body_html: @cjsg I met the same problem but I found it may be caused by the Anaconda, according to this issue. After upgrading the Anaconda to the latest version (Anaconda2-5.0.0.1), this problem solved. You can also try downgrading your conda to the older version.

body: @cjsg I met the same problem but I found it may be caused by the Anaconda, according to this [issue](http://github.com/conda/conda/issues/6030). After upgrading the Anaconda to the latest version (Anaconda2-5.0.0.1), this problem solved. You can also try downgrading your conda to the older version.
